Hello dearest readers,

I feel like everything has fallen apart. Everyone hates me and I don't know why. I wont even do any thing to any body and someone just stabs me in the back for who knows why. But I've realized something today, I only have four actual friends. You want to know  something im sure if there is someone reading this that hates me guess what, I cried for like four hours today and then now the blood vessels are all popped in my eyes. Do you know what it's like for you to hurt so much you can't sleep you can't function to pain properlly. Do you want to know what it feels like? Cause I can fucking show you so damn well!! Im so fucking emotional. Like everything can hurt me in some way. Im gonna ripp your heart at the seems so you know how I feel. I was so sad you know that I bit a chunk of my lip open. Also I didn't get no sleep and Im not gonna get any tomorrow. My eyes are so fucking weird looking. Do you know what it's like to have people see crying and then they ask whats wrong and you say im fine and then from there you have to go your whole day faking happieness. This is probally going to be a long entry. But hey who cares I don't. You shouldn't either cause you didn't fucking take your time to write it for nothing. Huh? Yeah thats what I fucking thought. I fled with suicide sometimes it kills the pain. I thought my life was like a fairy tale untill you broke me into a million peices. Hey I am so depressed it's not even funny. I wonder how many people would care if I died in the next couple hours. I wish today was one of those day where Im going to black out then wake up and hear the words " she's not gonna live!" Yeah thats my kind of fun beautiful beautiful!!!!!!! I know you don't care what I have to say but what if one of theses entries break out to be about how much I want you to die and how much I hate you for what you've just put me through. Huh? How would you feel then? Im asking a lot of questions aren't I but thats okay I love this entry it's got how I feel written all over it. From beginning to the end. Yeah normally I hide my feelings but screw it. Yeah i might be crazy nucka deal with it BITCH! Well this is all for now Ive got other things to do okay? yeah.... I would like some fucking comments on my fucking entry got it!!!!!!?????



-?

The tender kiss is the feeling where you can be anywhere and show your feelings.

You kill for
revenge.
That is because you have lost something or
someone you held very dear. Now you can't seem
to get over the loss that marked your soul, and
the only solution is to go after the one person
who brought all this pain to you. Chances are
you are angry inside and you bottle everything
up and don't talk to anyone about it. People
may want to help, but you think that they can
never understand your pain and only get
frustrated because of this. But it is important
to see all that you have left and be thankful
of that even if you have lost something great.
It may not be true that Times heals all wounds,
but with time and talking about your feelings,
maybe the hurt will ease.

Main weapon: Yourself
Quote: "You can close your eyes to
reality but not to memories" -Stainslaw J.
Lec
